### Order Service API

### Get all orders
GET http://localhost:9002/orders
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Submit new order
POST http://localhost:9002/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isbn": "1231231231",
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### Submit order with minimum quantity
POST http://localhost:9002/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isbn": "",
  "quantity": 1
}

###

### Submit order with maximum quantity
POST http://localhost:9002/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isbn": "9789876543210",
  "quantity": 5
}

